<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

  <head>
    <!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="registration.css"> -->

  </head>

  <body>

    <style>
      .container-fluid {
        background-color: white;

        padding: 50px;
      }

      .photo {
        display: flex;

      }

      .img {
        display: inline;

        width: 150px;

        /* border: solid; */
        border: 1px solid black;
        padding-top: 0px;
        padding-right: 30px;
        padding-bottom: 100px;
        padding-left: 30px;


      }

      .elements {
        padding: 0px;
        display: inline;
        border-bottom: 1px solid;
        border-bottom-color: black;


      }

      .field {

        color: black;
        padding-left: 00px;
        padding-right: 250px;

      }

      .new {

        color: black;
        padding-left: 00px;
        padding-right: 75%;
      }

      input[type=email] {
        border: 0px solid;
        height: 20px;
        width: 90%;
        padding-left: 10px;

      }

      .details {
        text-align: left;
        width: 300px;
        padding: 6px 10px;
        margin: 1px 0;
        /* box-sizing: unset; */
      }


      h5,
      h4 {
        margin-top: 1px;
      }

      /* input[type=text] {
        text-align: center;
        width: 160px;
        padding: 6px 10px;
        margin: 8px 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      } */

      #RegNo {
        text-align: center;
        width: 160px;
        padding: 6px 10px;
        margin: 8px 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      textarea {
        margin-top: 1px;
      }

      table {
        border-collapse: collapse;
        width: 70%;

      }

      th {
        height: 10px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      th,
      td {
        padding: 10px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .date_table {
        width: 100%;

      }

      .date_table td {
        text-align: justify;

      }

      .Signature_table {
        width: 100%;
      }
    </style>

    <form>
      <div class="container-fluid">

        <div class="photo">
          <div>
            <img src="" alt="" style="width: 3.5cm;height: 4.5cm;">
          </div>
          <div style="width: 70%;">
            <p style="text-align: center;"><em>Faculty of Applied Sciences</em></p>
            <p style="text-align: center;"><em>Wayamba University of Sri Lanka</em></p>
            <h4 align="center">Course Registration Form</h4>
            <p style="text-align: center;"><em>Acadamic Year: <%= data.personal.academicYear %> (Level
                <%= data.personal.level %> )</em> </p>
          </div>
        </div>


        <div align="right">
          <div style="display: inline-block;">
            <label for="RegNo">Reg No:</label>
            <input type="text" id="RegNo" name="username" value="<%= data.personal.regNo %>">
          </div>
        </div>


        <div>
          <div style="display: inline-block;">
            <label for="test">01. Name with initials(In block capitals):-</label>
            <label class="details"><%= data.personal.name %> </label>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p>02. Gender :- <em>Male / Female</em></p>
        <div>
          <div style="display: inline-block;">
            <label for="Title">02. Contact No. for Immediate Correspondence:-</label>
            <label class="details"><%= data.personal.contact %> </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p>04. Selected subject Combination:- (Mark (âœ“) the selected combination) </p>
        <table border="1px solid black" align="center">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th><em>Combination code</em></th>
              <th><em>Combination Discription</em></th>
              <th><em>Selected Combination</em></th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>Combination 1</td>
              <td>MATH & STAT + CMIS + ELTN </td>
              <td></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Combination 2</td>
              <td>MATH & STAT + ELTN + IMGT</td>
              <td></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Combination 3</td>
              <td>MATH & STAT + IMGT + CMIS </td>
              <td></td>
            </tr>

          </tbody>
        </table>
        <p>05. Please consult your Student Counselor before filling the following table:- </p>


        <table border="1px" align="center" style="page-break-after:always;">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <td align="center" colspan="3">SEMESTER I - COURSE MODULES</td>
          </thead>
          </tr>
          <tbody>
            <tr>

              <td><em>Module Code</em></td>
              <td><em>Title of the Module</em></td>
              <td><em>No. Credits</em></td>
            </tr>
            <% var sem1Mandatory=data.semester1.mandatory %>
            <% for( let i = 0; i < sem1Mandatory.length; i++ ) { %>
            <tr>
              <td style="vertical-align:middle"><%= sem1Mandatory[i].code %></td>
              <td style="vertical-align:middle"><%= sem1Mandatory[i].name %></td>
              <td style="vertical-align:middle"><%= sem1Mandatory[i].credit %></td>
            </tr>
            <% } %>
            <td></td>
            <td colspan="2"><em>Total No. of Credits For Semester I =</em></td>

            </tr>
          </tbody>
          <br>
        </table>
      </div>
      <div class="container-fluid">
        <br>

        <table border="1px" align="center">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <td align="center" colspan="3">SEMESTER II - COURSE MODULES</td>
          </thead>
          </tr>
          <tbody>
            <tr>

              <td><em>Module Code</em></td>
              <td><em>Title of the Module</em></td>
              <td><em>No. Credits</em></td>
            </tr>
            <% var sem2Mandatory=data.semester2.mandatory %>
            <% for( let i = 0; i < sem2Mandatory.length; i++ ) { %>
            <tr>
              <td style="vertical-align:middle"><%= sem2Mandatory[i].code %></td>
              <td style="vertical-align:middle"><%= sem2Mandatory[i].name %></td>
              <td style="vertical-align:middle"><%= sem2Mandatory[i].credit %></td>
            </tr>
            <% } %>

            <tr>
              <th></th>
              <td colspan="2"><em>Total No. of Credits For Semester II =</em></td>

            <tr>
              <td colspan="3"><em>Total Number of Credits For Academic Year =</em></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
        <br>
        <p>04. Registration Fee: Rs. 150</p>
        <table class="date_table">
          <tr>
            <td>Date of Payments:</td>
            <td>Receipt No:</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Date: .....................................</td>
            <td>.................................</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td></td>
            <td>Signature of Applicant</td>
          </tr>
          <tr></tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Date: .....................................</td>
            <td>.................................</td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td></td>
            <td>Signature of Mentor</td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        </br>
        <hr>
        <p>I certify that the above student has selected the correct set of modules relevant to his/her combination at
          Level 2 and that he/she will fulfill the minimum annual credit requirement in respect of the subject area(s)
          offered by my Department. </p>
        </br>
        </br>
        <table class="Signature_table">
          <tr>
            <td>..................................................</td>
            <td>..................................................</td>
            <td>..................................................</td>
            <td>..................................................</td>

          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Signature of the Head/Academic Advisor/CMIS</td>
            <td>Signature of the Head/Academic Advisor/ELTN</td>
            <td>Signature of the Head/Academic Advisor/IMGT</td>
            <td>Signature of the Head/Academic Advisor/MATH</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Date...........................................</td>
            <td>Date...........................................</td>
            <td>Date...........................................</td>
            <td>Date...........................................</td>

          </tr>
        </table>
        </br>
        <p>I certify that the above student has selected modules required minimum/maximum aggregating to the number of
          credits(30/33) for Level 3</p>
        </br>
        <p>.........................................................</p>
        <p>Signature of the Student Counsellor</p>

      </div>
    </form>
  </body>

</html>